# Editor cruft
*.swp
*.bak
.direnv/
result
result-*

# Per-machine hardware-configs are placeholders in git, overwritten by
# install.sh at install time. We KEEP the placeholders so `nix flake check`
# evaluates everywhere. If you want to commit a real one for reinstall
# convenience, just `git add -f hosts/<host>/hardware-configuration.nix`.
